22#include "mpc-impl.h"
23
24int
25mpc_urandom (mpc_ptr a, gmp_randstate_t state)
26{
27 int r, i;
28
29 r = mpfr_urandomb (mpc_realref(a), state);
30 i = mpfr_urandomb (mpc_imagref(a), state);
31 return r && i;
32}
